\begin_inset Formula $\ccsIdentifier P_{o}\weakSimEq\ccsIdentifier P_{g}$
\end_inset

, but also 
\begin_inset Formula $\ccsIdentifier P_{o}\weakSimEq\ccsIdentifier P_{t}$
\end_inset

.
